{
  "texts": [
    "It has recently performed on law school exams [11] and solved questions on medical exams [24].",
    "While it has contributed to a paradigm shift in educational space [48], it also has the potential to significantly impact teaching and learning [4,55], in addition to ethics, plagiarism, and academic integrity in higher education [38,46,47].",
    "While ChatGPT has gained popularity in educational arena, limited research has been explored the use of ChatGPT within restricted access areas.",
    "Given ChatGPT is not directly accessible in Hong Kong, its utilization necessitates Virtual Private Network (VPN) access or the procurement of a ChatGPT license for students use within schools [13].",
    "This study aims to examine the use of ChatGPT specifically within public universities in Hong Kong."
  ]
}